OL,5, A convicted double murderer who had    
OL,6, been released on licence battered his  
OL,7, neighbour to death with a coffee table,
OL,8, a jury has heard.                      
OL,10,FLawrence Bierton was jailed in 1996 for
OL,11,Fthe murders of two sisters.            
OL,13,FAfter being released in 2017 and       
OL,14,Frecalled to prison in 2018, Bierton was
OL,15,Freleased on licence again in 2020.     
OL,17,FIn November 2021, Pauline Quinn, 73,   
OL,18,Fwas found dead at her home. Bierton    
OL,19,Fdenies her murder on the grounds of    
OL,20,Fdiminished responsibility.             
